{"__ud_title":"Nanobot：轻量级 AI 助手完整使用教程","__ud_tags":["openclaw","nanobot"],"__ud_update_time":1770792294277,"__ud_create_time":1770765729264,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Nanobot轻量级-AI-助手完整使用教程"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Nanobot：轻量级 AI 助手完整使用教程"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nanobot 是香港大学数据智能实验室开源的超轻量级个人 AI 助手，仅约 4000 行代码完整复刻了OpenClaw 智能体的核心功能。Nanobot具备网页搜索、文件操作、定时任务、记忆机制等能力，支持 24 小时实时行情分析、全栈开发、日程管理和个人知识库等场景。相比原版 43 万行代码，Nanobot 用 99% 的代码精简实现同等生产力，开发者几小时即可通读源码，快速理解 AI 调用工具与管理记忆的底层逻辑，是学习和定制 Agent 的理想选择。"}]},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"/post-assets/mlhdb091-image.png","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Nanobot的主要功能"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nanobot的主要功能"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"智能体核心"},{"type":"text","text":"：基于大语言模型实现自主任务规划、工具调用与多轮对话的完整闭环。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"信息获取"},{"type":"text","text":"：集成网页搜索接口，支持实时检索外部信息进行分析处理。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"文件操作"},{"type":"text","text":"：提供代码读写与文件系统管理能力，可构建本地化个人知识库。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"通讯集成"},{"type":"text","text":"：原生支持 Telegram 和 WhatsApp，实现跨平台消息收发与远程交互。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"定时任务"},{"type":"text","text":"：内置类 Cron 调度系统，可按预设周期自动执行提醒与任务。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"记忆机制"},{"type":"text","text":"：采用持久化存储方案，保存对话上下文以支持长期记忆回溯。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"语音交互"},{"type":"text","text":"：接入 Groq Whisper 服务，实现语音消息的自动识别与转录。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景模板"},{"type":"text","text":"：预置金融分析、开发助手、日程管理、知识问答四类即用型应用模板。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Nanobot的技术原理"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nanobot的技术原理"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"极简架构设计"},{"type":"text","text":"：Nanobot 将系统拆解为四个核心模块——Agent 循环负责协调大语言模型与工具之间的交互执行，记忆模块实现对话上下文的持久化存储与检索，技能加载器支持动态扩展功能组件，消息总线统一处理内外部通讯路由，整体用显式依赖注入替代复杂抽象层。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agent 执行流程"},{"type":"text","text":"：用户输入首先经过 Prompt 构建器组装上下文，随后送入大语言模型进行推理决策，模型自主判断需调用的工具并生成执行指令，工具执行完成后将结果反馈至模型，最终更新记忆状态，形成”感知-决策-行动-学习”的完整闭环。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"多源 LLM 接入"},{"type":"text","text":"：系统通过 OpenRouter 实现统一路由，可无缝切换 Claude、GPT、Gemini 等云端模型，同时兼容本地 vLLM 部署方案，满足灵活选型需求，支持私有化场景下的数据安全要求。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"动态工具系统"},{"type":"text","text":"：所有功能用技能模块形式置于 skills/ 目录，运行时自动加载，内置涵盖代码操作、网络请求、系统命令等常用工具，开发者遵循统一接口规范即可快速扩展自定义能力。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"跨平台通讯层"},{"type":"text","text":"：Telegram 基于官方 Bot API 实现消息收发，WhatsApp 采用 Web 协议桥接方案，所有渠道消息经内部总线标准化后分发至 Agent 处理，确保多平台体验一致性。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Nanobot的项目地址"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nanobot的项目地址"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"GitHub仓库"},{"type":"text","text":"："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://github.com/HKUDS/nanobot","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"https://github.com/HKUDS/nanobot"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Nanobot的应用场景"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nanobot的应用场景"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"金融实时分析"},{"type":"text","text":"：Nanobot 能7×24 小时监控市场行情，自动抓取数据生成投资洞察报告。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"全栈开发辅助"},{"type":"text","text":"：支持随时执行代码编写、调试、部署任务，充当随身技术合伙人。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"智能日程管理"},{"type":"text","text":"：Nanobot 能自动安排会议、发送提醒、处理待办，协调个人时间规划。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"个人知识库"},{"type":"text","text":"：Nanobot 支持整合 PDF、笔记等私有文档，支持自然语言问答与知识检索。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"远程随身助手"},{"type":"text","text":"：通过 Telegram 或 WhatsApp 随时随地交互，无需常驻电脑前。"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Nanobot与OpenClaw对比"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Nanobot与OpenClaw对比"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码量对比：Nanobot约4000行，OpenClaw约43万行"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"启动速度：Nanobot只需3秒左右，OpenClaw需要30秒"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"内存占用：Nanobot低于100MB，OpenClaw约1GB"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"架构设计：Nanobot采用微内核模块化架构，OpenClaw是单体架构"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"部署难度：Nanobot非常简单，OpenClaw相对复杂"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"适用人群：Nanobot适合普通用户和研究者，OpenClaw更适合高级开发者"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"快速部署指南5分钟搞定"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"快速部署指南（5分钟搞定）"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第一步安装"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第一步：安装"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式A：pip直接安装（最简单）"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"pip install nanobot-ai"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式B：使用uv安装（更快）"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"uv tool install nanobot-ai"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式C：源码安装（想二次开发选这个）"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"git clone https://github.com/HKUDS/nanobot.git\ncd nanobot\npip install -e ."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第二步初始化配置"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第二步：初始化配置"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"运行初始化命令，创建配置文件："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"nanobot onboard"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这会在你的用户目录下创建 ~/.nanobot/ 文件夹，包含配置文件和工作目录。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"第三步配置API密钥"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第三步：配置API密钥"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编辑配置文件 ~/.nanobot/config.json："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"openrouter\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-or-v1-xxx\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-opus-4-5\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"webSearch\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"BSA-xxx\"\n  }\n}"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置说明："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ope